item.title: CVE-2022-23922|2024-09-16T19:37:00.261Z -- win-911 -- win-911
item.description: WIN-911 2021 R1 and R2 are vulnerable to a permissions misconfiguration that may allow an attacker to locally write files to the Program Announcer directory and elevate permissions whenever the program is executed.
